text: Maicol Gabriel Cabrera Galain (born May 11, 1996 in Maldonado, Uruguay) is a professional Uruguayan footballer who currently plays for Tampico Madero F.C. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Uruguayan footballers Category:Uruguayan expatriate footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Tampico Madero F.C. footballers Category:Ascenso MX players Category:Liga Premier de México players Category:People from Maldonado Department Category:Uruguayan expatriate sportspeople in Mexico Category:Expatriate footballers in Mexico
